[Start]
    |
    |--> [Initialize Variables]
    |       - BestDeciphered = null
    |       - BestScore = minimum possible value
    |
    |--> [For each possible Offset]
    |       |
    |       |--> [For each possible Block Length]
    |               |
    |               |--> [Decipher the String using current Offset and Block Length]
    |               |
    |               |--> [Score the Deciphered String based on punctuation/capitalization]
    |               |       |
    |               |       |--> [Is this score better than the BestScore?]
    |               |               |
    |               |               |-- [Yes] --> Update BestScore and BestDeciphered
    |               |               |
    |               |               |-- [No] --> Continue to next Block Length
    |               |
    |               |--> [Repeat with next Block Length]
    |
    |--> [Repeat with next Offset]
    |
    |--> [Return BestDeciphered as the result]
    |
[End]
